  • Constructor Details

    • Property

      public Property(String name, int space, int purchase, int rent, int mortgage, double rentIncreaseRate, String color, int oneHouse, boolean owned)
      Constructor used to set each property for the game. Values -1 or "NA" means that the specification it is associated * with is not applicable for that property type.
      Parameters:
      name - name of the property
      space - the space on the board
      purchase - purchase price of the property
      rent - rent price of the property
      mortgage - price to mortgage the property
      rentIncreaseRate - the rate rent increases when homes are * added to the property
      color - color of the property
      oneHouse - price of one house to place on the property
      owned - boolean representing if owned or not
